{"tid":2256840,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人生冇意義了","createTime":"2020-10-24T16:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T17:58:05.000Z","uid":21355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ddf7ef46b86ce70d1065609624e72791e602cfce","tid":2256840,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7beef5160e24009c382e78f232aca5695d4402","tid":2256840,"uid":256205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3OeQzST.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3OeQzST.png&h=17701515&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd3c17409725d5e29cac31bf8e2bed81a7f20374","tid":2256840,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:31:26.000Z","msg":"打jj"},{"pid":"6da5e95ec2c13e40a82037acea468f092cf033ef","tid":2256840,"uid":370010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:39:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"501961254ea4188f60b70faf239e364066d6d5be","tid":2256840,"uid":76542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:44:44.000Z","msg":"哲學上黎講<br />\n人生既意義可以分為主觀同客觀<br />\n<br />\n主觀黎講<br />\n阿德勒係提倡可以直接主觀咁去賦予意義<br />\n即係你屙個屎咁<br />\n你話佢係有意義就係有意義<br />\n所以人生既意義<br />\n係有無限個可以主觀賦予既機會<br />\n不論任何大小既人、事、物，都可以<br />\n所以你話人生無意義<br />\n你就咁呼吸你都可以話你係有意義<br />\n<br />\n再唔係落返道家思想<br />\n客觀咁講<br />\n老子提倡<br />\n人類生存本來就係有意義<br />\n但哩個意義你自己係唔知既<br />\n第三方覺得你有價值你就係有意義<br />\n例如<br />\n有個極度孤獨既人想望到一個人<br />\n而你咁岩係佢身邊行過<br />\n咁你人生就已經係有意義<br />\n因為你既存在令到其他人感到愉快<br />\n即你既存在令人感到有價值，利他<br />\n咁你客觀上黎講就係有人生意義<br />\n<br />\n總結黎講無論主觀定客觀<br />\n你人生都係有意義<br />\n<br />\n所以咪再開post"},{"pid":"6d4b6fe8ab7876b2266a67c96cc7da5fc2b0714c","tid":2256840,"uid":315852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:48:51.000Z","msg":"樓豬全部啲post都好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70b4b68c0fe422b0d318bc754eecd3704ceb097","tid":2256840,"uid":165341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6da5e95ec2c13e40a82037acea468f092cf033ef","tid":2256840,"uid":370010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:39:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T17:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a78fa8badaac6aa232b2245517081af93b3d8c6","tid":2256840,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d4b6fe8ab7876b2266a67c96cc7da5fc2b0714c","tid":2256840,"uid":315852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:48:51.000Z","msg":"樓豬全部啲post都好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T18:33:17.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"f84cae49461c1b4e9afbd6d10a7f2f94f7528478","tid":2256840,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6da5e95ec2c13e40a82037acea468f092cf033ef","tid":2256840,"uid":370010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:39:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:18:42.000Z","msg":"who funson9"},{"pid":"28d9a298a9881533610da757a626d077499010f8","tid":2256840,"uid":370010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:58:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}